These are Puzzles for 3x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-1::.
There are 2 different nationalities: argentine, egyptian
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: lacrosse, surfing
The people use 2 different means of transport: train, airplane
1. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the right of the person driving the train##1
2. the egyptian is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |
| Nationality   | egyptian    | argentine |
| Sport         | surfing | lacrosse    |
| Transport     | train     | airplane      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: cola, fanta
There are 2 different nationalities: polish, malaysian
The people use 2 different means of transport: airplane, snowmobile
1. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
2. the polish is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |
| Beverage      | fanta  | cola   |
| Nationality   | malaysian | polish  |
| Transport     | snowmobile   | airplane |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-3::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: camping, hiking
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: family, satire
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: baseball, cycling
1. the person who's hobby is hiking is in an even position##4
2. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |
| Hobby         | camping   | hiking  |
| Movie-Genre   | satire | family  |
| Sport         | baseball   | cycling |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-4::.
