The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: western, comedy
The people use 2 different means of transport: bus, helicopter
1. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
2. the person eating banana is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |
| Food          | banana | tomato |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy   | western   |
| Transport     | helicopter       | bus      |

