.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-7::.
There 2 different types of food: papaya, grapefruit
The people have 2 different jobs:  engineer, videographer
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: surfing, climbing
1. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left of the engineer##1
2. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is climbing##3
3. the person eating papaya is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |
| Food    | grapefruit | papaya     |
| Job     | videographer | engineer |
| Sport   | climbing | surfing    |

 #################################

 
