.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-15::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: chess, camping
There are 2 different nationalities: pakistani, japanese
2 different pets are kept: turtle, chinchilla
1. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
2. the pakistani is on the left of the japanese##1
3. the person who's hobby is chess is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |
| Hobby         | camping | chess |
| Nationality   | pakistani     | japanese     |
| Pet           | chinchilla          | turtle     |

